# Esiana Design Philosophy

Source: [design-philosophy.md](../../design-philosophy.md). Enforcement docs: [density-doctrine.md](../../docs/density-doctrine.md), [deprecated-ui-patterns.md](../../docs/deprecated-ui-patterns.md), [design-philosophy-checklist.md](../../docs/design-philosophy-checklist.md), [terminology.md](../../docs/terminology.md).

## Mandatory for new UI

- **Do not introduce** patterns listed in [deprecated-ui-patterns.md](../../docs/deprecated-ui-patterns.md)
- Follow hard limits in [density-doctrine.md](../../docs/density-doctrine.md)
- User-facing terms from [terminology.md](../../docs/terminology.md) — **Campaign Home** not Dashboard; Game Master / Writer not Steward / Co-DM in UI

## Principles

- Reader-first; calm density; typography-over-borders; progressive disclosure
- Ultrawide: breathing room and measure caps — not more panels or columns
- Play-first: mid-session usable; continuity aids play, does not museum-ify it
- Do **not** require Steward or Chronicle for operational surfaces

## Codex interaction

```txt
Mode:   Reading | Writing
Layout: Standard | Wide
```

Immersive = focus overlay toggle (`BlockFocusOverlay`), not a persistent top-level workspace mode.

